    "DisplayTitle": "Minor Repairs Needed: Remote Outpost near ~mission(NearbyLocation)",
    "Description": "A nearby outpost of ours at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> is suffering from some mechanical failures and could use repairing. Our usual technician is off on another job so we're looking to hire an outside contractor.\n\nWe will need <EM4>three fuses replaced</EM4> and if you could bring a <EM4>salvaging tool</EM4> with <EM4>enough canisters of RMC to fix around three pipes</EM4> that should take care of the rest.\n\nIf you need more information on maintenance work, see <EM4>\u201cCornerstone Developments' Guide to Maintenance\u201d</EM4> entry in your mobiGlas Journal.\n\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
